#2. Write a method for increment and decrement operators(++, --)
a=5
for i in range(a):
  a+=1
  print('Increment',a)
  a-=2
  print('Decrement',a)
----------------------------------------------------------------
>>>  Increment 6
      Decrement 4
      Increment 5
      Decrement 3
      Increment 4
      Decrement 2
      Increment 3
      Decrement 1
      Increment 2
      Decrement 0

