#3. Write a program to find the two numbers equal or not.
a=int(input('enter any number '))
b=int(input('enter 2nd number '))
if a==b:
  print('Both are equal')
else:
  print('Both are not equal')
------------------------------------------------------------------
>>>   enter any number 67
      enter 2nd number 45
      Both are not equal


